sors. As soon as Goomy pick up any sign of enemies, they go into hiding. This is how they\u2019ve survived."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "The weakest of all Dragon-type Pok\u00e9mon, it\u2019s unable to breathe if its skin dries out, so it sticks to shady places."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "Because most of its body is water, it will dry up if the weather becomes too arid. It\u2019s considered the weakest dragon Pok\u00e9mon."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Its body is mostly water. If it dries out, it will die, so it\u2019s always sitting with perfect stillness in the shade."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It uses its horns to check out its surroundings. They\u2019re very sensitive, so if you grab them, it will feel a strong shock and be unable to move."}, {"version": "x", "text": "The weakest Dragon-type Pok\u00e9mon, it lives in damp, shady places, so its body doesn\u2019t dry out."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It\u2019s covered in a slimy membrane that makes any punches or kicks slide off it harmlessly."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "legends-arceus", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["legends-arceus", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "goomy"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "sliggoo"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "goodra"}]}